# 🎮 Life RPG

Turn your real life into a game — track habits, complete quests, and level up yourself.

# 📌 Overview

Life RPG is a gamified productivity web application that transforms everyday tasks and habits into an engaging role-playing experience.
Instead of traditional to-do lists, users complete real-life "quests", earn rewards,
and track their progress as they level up in their personal growth journey.
The goal of the project is to make self-improvement more motivating, interactive,
and enjoyable by combining game mechanics with productivity tools in a modern full-stack web application.

Users can:

* Complete real-life tasks as "quests"
* Earn rewards and level up
* Track progress visually
* Stay motivated through game mechanics

Built during a hackathon to make self-improvement engaging and addictive.

# ✨ Features

* 🧩 Quest-based task system
* 📈 Progress tracking and leveling
* 🎯 Habit and goal management
* 🎨 Modern responsive UI
* ⚡ Real-time updates
* 🔐 User authentication system

# 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend**

* React
* Tailwind CSS
* Vite
* Framer Motion

**Backend**

* Node.js
* Express.js

**Database**

* PostgreSQL
* Drizzle ORM

**Other Tools**

* React Query
* Zod (validation)
* Passport (authentication)

